T1  - Inflationary regimes and relative price variability: evidence from Argentina
AU  - Dabús, Carlos
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 62
IS  - 2
SP  - 535
EP  - 547
PY  - 2000
DA  - 2000/08/01/
SN  - 0304-3878
